      • getDomainResultResultJavaType

        public Class<T> getDomainResultResultJavaType()
        Description copied from interface: RowReader
        The type actually returned from this reader's RowReader.readRow(org.hibernate.sql.results.jdbc.spi.RowProcessingState, org.hibernate.sql.results.jdbc.spi.JdbcValuesSourceProcessingOptions) call, accounting for any transformers.

        May be null to indicate that no transformation is applied.

        Ultimately intended for use in comparing values are being de-duplicated

        Specified by:
